    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 提前获得第五艘星际飞船发射许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/spacex-wins-earlier-than-expected-approval-to-fly-fifth-starship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SpaceX 获得了美国航空安全监管机构的批准，将对其大型星际飞船火箭进行第五次重大试飞——这是一项关键任务，助推器部分将返回太空并尝试直立着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/spacex-wins-earlier-than-expected-approval-to-fly-fifth-starship</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 17:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国金融科技公司敦促政府支持增长和 IPO 梦想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/uk-s-fintech-darlings-push-government-to-back-growth-ipo-dreams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国一些最有价值和增长最快的金融科技公司的高管警告工党政府，如果英国不能解决该行业的一些关键问题，包括股票上市和监管机构决策速度方面的挑战，伦敦可能会在金融科技领域落后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/uk-s-fintech-darlings-push-government-to-back-growth-ipo-dreams</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 09:02:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
